financial_analysis.prompt:
Perform a detailed financial analysis for this real estate investment:

Property Information:
{property_info}

Financial Details:
Purchase Price: {purchase_price}
Down Payment: {down_payment}
Loan Terms: {loan_terms}
Expected Rental Income: {rental_income}
Monthly Expenses: {monthly_expenses}
Expected Appreciation: {appreciation_rate}

Calculate and provide:
1. Cash flow analysis (monthly and annual)
2. Return on Investment (ROI)
3. Cap rate calculation
4. Break-even analysis
5. 5-year and 10-year projections
6. Risk assessment
7. Comparison with alternative investments

Present findings in a clear, actionable format with recommendations.
